'''Capital ship turrets''' (also known as '''capital turrets''', or informally, '''cap turrets''') were [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]] commonly mounted on [[Starship/Legends|starships]] and [[Space station/Legends|space stations]] for defense against [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]]. They were presumably similar to, or possibly a variant of, the [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolaser]].

Both the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] and [[Sabaoth Squadron/Legends|Sabaoth Squadron]] made use of capital ship turrets. Several defended [[Spacestation 1138]] in the [[Karthakk system]], and each [[Sabaoth destroyer|Sabaoth Destroyer]] was armed with six turrets, in addition to standard [[Laser turret/Legends|laser turrets]]. These weapons were powerful enough to pose a threat to [[Mere cruiser]]s, and during the orbital [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]], [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] and her [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] made it their priority to destroy all capital turrets on three Sabaoth Destroyers in order to aid the [[Mere Resistance]].

